Hello, I am trying to use the "related_blog_posts" tag provided, and supply tags, however these tags come from an array I added as a field, which I join as a string. I am not sure how to pass the string as param, neither of the 2 ways I am trying seems to be working:
```{% related_blog_posts limit=2, tags="tags_to_filter", post_formatter="related_post", no_wrapper=True %}
{% related_blog_posts limit=2, tags=tags_to_filter, post_formatter="related_post", no_wrapper=True %} -&gt; no quotes?```
